10 weapons in State buildings
11 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
12 Sec. 1. 13 V.S.A. § 4028 is added to read
13 § 4028. POSSESSION OF FIREARMS AND DANGEROUS WEAPONS IN
14 STATE BUILDINGS PROHIBITED
15 (a) A person shall not knowingly possess a firearm or dangerous weapon in
16 a State building.
17 (b)(1) A person who violates subsection (a) of this section shall be
18 imprisoned for not more than one year or fined not more than $2,000.00, or
19 both.
